Company Overview of Credit Suisse Next Investors, LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Credit Suisse Next Investors, LLC specializes in startup and later stage investments in financial technology and financial services companies. The fund seeks to invest between $10 million and $20 million.


One Madison AvenueNew York, NY 10010-3629United StatesFounded in 2013



