Experienced Growth Investors in Technology Companies Used by the Financial Services Industry






Information for Existing Investors




        Client login site








Who We Are
NEXT Investors identifies minority growth equity investment opportunities in private technology and services companies globally where the team has domain expertise and actionable edge. Our portfolio comprises high-growth private businesses that interact with the financial services industry.






Contact




        NEXT Investors








We focus on several business sectors:

Market Structure
Data Providers and Big Data Analytics
Enterprise Software
Tech-Enabled Finance
Other






The principals have been investing together at Credit Suisse for over 16 years.
Partnership with Credit Suisse
NEXT Investors leverages the global resources of Credit Suisse and the team’s extensive network to provide:

Exposure to global, organic sourcing channels
Access to differentiated dilligence resources and the insights of a Fortune 500 IT customer
Ability to drive growth in portfolio companies through preferred exposure to Credit Suisse clients and partners













